{"prompt": "Build a captivating website for a luxury car rental service. The design should prominently display a deep maroon.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Elite Wheels Luxury Rentals</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #2a0000; /* Deep Maroon */\n            color: #ffffff;\n            scroll-behavior: smooth;\n        }\n        header {\n            background: linear-gradient(to right, #2a0000, #5c0000); /* Deep Maroon to slightly lighter maroon */\n            padding: 20px 50px;\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: space-between;\n            align-items: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);\n        }\n        .logo {\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);\n        }\n        nav ul {\n            list-style: none;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            display: flex;\n        }\n        nav ul li {\n            margin-left: 30px;\n        }\n        nav ul li a {\n            text-decoration: none;\n            color: #ffffff;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        nav ul li a:hover {\n            color: #e0c3c3; /* Lighter shade for hover */\n        }\n        .hero {\n            background: url('https://via.placeholder.com/1500x800/2a0000/ffffff?text=Luxury+Cars') no-repeat center center/cover;\n            height: 80vh;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            text-align: center;\n            position: relative;\n        }\n        .hero::before {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            right: 0;\n            bottom: 0;\n            background: rgba(42, 0, 0, 0.7); /* Overlay for better text readability */\n        }\n        .hero h1 {\n            font-size: 4em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            z-index: 1;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);\n        }\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.8em;\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n            z-index: 1;\n            text-shadow: 1px 1px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);\n        }\n        .cta-button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: #e0c3c3; /* Lighter shade */\n            color: #2a0000; /* Deep Maroon text */\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            font-size: 1.4em;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;\n            border: 2px solid #e0c3c3;\n        }\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: #2a0000; /* Deep Maroon background on hover */\n            color: #e0c3c3; /* Lighter shade text on hover */\n            transform: translateY(-3px);\n        }\n        section {\n            padding: 80px 50px;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        h2 {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n            color: #e0c3c3; /* Lighter shade for headings */\n            text-shadow: 1px 1px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);\n        }\n        .car-gallery {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));\n            gap: 30px;\n        }\n        .car-item {\n            background-color: #3a0000; /* Slightly lighter than body */\n            padding: 20px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .car-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);\n        }\n        .car-item img {\n            max-width: 100%;\n            height: 200px;\n            object-fit: cover;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n        }\n        .car-item h3 {\n            font-size: 1.8em;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n            color: #e0c3c3; /* Lighter shade */\n        }\n        .car-item p {\n            font-size: 1em;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        footer {\n            background-color: #1a0000; /* Even darker maroon */\n            color: #cccccc;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 40px 50px;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n        footer p {\n            margin: 5px 0;\n        }\n        footer a {\n            color: #e0c3c3;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        footer a:hover {\n            color: #ffffff;\n        }\n        .contact-form {\n            background-color: #3a0000;\n            padding: 40px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);\n            display: inline-block;\n            text-align: left;\n        }\n        .contact-form input,\n        .contact-form textarea {\n            width: calc(100% - 20px);\n            padding: 12px;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            border: 1px solid #5c0000;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            background-color: #2a0000;\n            color: #ffffff;\n            font-size: 1em;\n        }\n        .contact-form button {\n            background-color: #e0c3c3;\n            color: #2a0000;\n            padding: 12px 25px;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .contact-form button:hover {\n            background-color: #2a0000;\n            color: #e0c3c3;\n            transform: translateY(-2px);\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"logo\">Elite Wheels</div>\n        <nav>\n            <ul>\n                <li><a href=\"#home\">Home</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"#fleet\">Fleet</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a></li>\n            </ul>\n        </nav>\n    </header>\n\n    <section id=\"home\" class=\"hero\">\n        <h1>Experience Unrivaled Luxury</h1>\n        <p>Drive the dream. Explore the world with unparalleled style.</p>\n        <a href=\"#fleet\" class=\"cta-button\">View Our Fleet</a>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"fleet\">\n        <h2>Our Exquisite Collection</h2>\n        <div class=\"car-gallery\">\n            <div class=\"car-item\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/5c0000/ffffff?text=Rolls-Royce+Phantom\" alt=\"Rolls-Royce Phantom\">\n                <h3>Rolls-Royce Phantom</h3>\n                <p>The epitome of automotive craftsmanship. Experience serene luxury and commanding presence.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"car-item\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/5c0000/ffffff?text=Lamborghini+Aventador\" alt=\"Lamborghini Aventador\">\n                <h3>Lamborghini Aventador</h3>\n                <p>Unleash raw power and breathtaking design. For those who demand exhilaration.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"car-item\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/5c0000/ffffff?text=Mercedes-Benz+S-Class\" alt=\"Mercedes-Benz S-Class\">\n                <h3>Mercedes-Benz S-Class</h3>\n                <p>The benchmark of modern luxury sedans. Intelligent, sophisticated, and supremely comfortable.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"car-item\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/5c0000/ffffff?text=Bentley+Continental+GT\" alt=\"Bentley Continental GT\">\n                <h3>Bentley Continental GT</h3>\n                <p>A perfect fusion of grand touring performance and exquisite luxury. Effortlessly stylish.</p>\n            </div>\n             <div class=\"car-item\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/5c0000/ffffff?text=Ferrari+488+GTB\" alt=\"Ferrari 488 GTB\">\n                <h3>Ferrari 488 GTB</h3>\n                <p>Iconic Italian passion meets cutting-edge engineering. Experience pure driving pleasure.</p>\n            </div>\n             <div class=\"car-item\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/5c0000/ffffff?text=Porsche+911+Carrera\" alt=\"Porsche 911 Carrera\">\n                <h3>Porsche 911 Carrera</h3>\n                <p>Timeless sports car design with exhilarating performance. An icon for a reason.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"contact\">\n        <h2>Reserve Your Experience</h2>\n        <div class=\"contact-form\">\n            <form action=\"#\" method=\"post\">\n                <input type=\"text\" name=\"name\" placeholder=\"Your Name\" required>\n                <input type=\"email\" name=\"email\" placeholder=\"Your Email\" required>\n                <input type=\"tel\" name=\"phone\" placeholder=\"Your Phone Number\" required>\n                <textarea name=\"message\" rows=\"4\" placeholder=\"Your Message or Inquiry\" required></textarea>\n                <button type=\"submit\">Send Inquiry</button>\n            </form>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Elite Wheels Luxury Rentals. All rights reserved.</p>\n        <p>Contact us: <a href=\"mailto:info@elitewheels.com\">info@elitewheels.com</a> | <a href=\"tel:+1234567890\">+1 (234) 567-890</a></p>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        document.querySelectorAll('a[href^=\"#\"]').forEach(anchor => {\n            anchor.addEventListener('click', function (e) {\n                e.preventDefault();\n\n                document.querySelector(this.getAttribute('href')).scrollIntoView({\n                    behavior: 'smooth'\n                });\n            });\n        });\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>"}